{
  "video_id": "7g-BLzjEbXU",
  "title": "Corporate Culture",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 910.0,
      "end_time": 3993.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] This is Duke University."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13790.0,
      "end_time": 15157.0,
      "text": "- I&#39;d like to tell you about a research project"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15157.0,
      "end_time": 17591.0,
      "text": "on corporate culture that I&#39;ve been working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17591.0,
      "end_time": 20944.0,
      "text": "with Cam Harvey and Jill Popadak from Duke"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20944.0,
      "end_time": 23898.0,
      "text": "and Shiv Rajgopal from Columbia University."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23898.0,
      "end_time": 26348.0,
      "text": "This project&#39;s been supoorted by the COLE Center here"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26348.0,
      "end_time": 28848.0,
      "text": "at Fuqua, and by CFO Magazine."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30270.0,
      "end_time": 32731.0,
      "text": "Now if you read the headlines, you see corporate culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32731.0,
      "end_time": 34999.0,
      "text": "often gets blamed or gets credit"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34999.0,
      "end_time": 37890.0,
      "text": "for dramatic corporate events."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37890.0,
      "end_time": 39890.0,
      "text": "So for example the VW emissions scandal"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39900.0,
      "end_time": 41983.0,
      "text": "and recent events at Wells Fargo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41983.0,
      "end_time": 43873.0,
      "text": "we read about corporate culture leading"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43874.0,
      "end_time": 46590.0,
      "text": "to maybe a bad outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46590.0,
      "end_time": 48384.0,
      "text": "With Google, corporate culture gets at least some"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48384.0,
      "end_time": 50705.0,
      "text": "of the credit for Google having such a fantastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50705.0,
      "end_time": 52733.0,
      "text": "and successful company."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52734.0,
      "end_time": 54834.0,
      "text": "So corporate culture is everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54834.0,
      "end_time": 57205.0,
      "text": "and I have to admit I approached this research project"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57205.0,
      "end_time": 58960.0,
      "text": "as a bit of a skeptic."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58960.0,
      "end_time": 61124.0,
      "text": "What exactly is this corporate culture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61124.0,
      "end_time": 64831.0,
      "text": "Is it really as important as these headlines say it is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64831.0,
      "end_time": 66936.0,
      "text": "And if it is, how does it work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66936.0,
      "end_time": 68576.0,
      "text": "These are questions that I wanted to answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68576.0,
      "end_time": 71789.0,
      "text": "and our research team wanted to try to answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71790.0,
      "end_time": 73911.0,
      "text": "So what we did is we went out and surveyed"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73911.0,
      "end_time": 76702.0,
      "text": "1,900 CEOs and CFOs"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76965.0,
      "end_time": 78924.0,
      "text": "from around the globe"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78924.0,
      "end_time": 80682.0,
      "text": "to ask them about corporate culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80682.0,
      "end_time": 81894.0,
      "text": "What they think of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81894.0,
      "end_time": 83726.0,
      "text": "How it works at their companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83726.0,
      "end_time": 86908.0,
      "text": "We also interviewed companies one-on-one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86908.0,
      "end_time": 89613.0,
      "text": "executives from companies one-on-one, that represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89613.0,
      "end_time": 92553.0,
      "text": "the 20% of the market capitalization"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92553.0,
      "end_time": 95540.0,
      "text": "of the U.S. stock exchanges."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95550.0,
      "end_time": 97352.0,
      "text": "So we had quite a large number of companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97352.0,
      "end_time": 100555.0,
      "text": "and a lot of depth and importance of those companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100555.0,
      "end_time": 104259.0,
      "text": "Now it took 50 MBA students as research assistants"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104259.0,
      "end_time": 106100.0,
      "text": "to help us pull this off."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106100.0,
      "end_time": 108760.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re really thankful for that help"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108760.0,
      "end_time": 110869.0,
      "text": "and we couldn&#39;t have done it without them."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110869.0,
      "end_time": 113945.0,
      "text": "Alright, first question: is corporate culture important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113945.0,
      "end_time": 115901.0,
      "text": "Yes, executives tell us resoundingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115901.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "corporate culture is very important"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 121646.0,
      "text": "and it affects many parts of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121647.0,
      "end_time": 123518.0,
      "text": "So we went about trying to address this"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123518.0,
      "end_time": 125350.0,
      "text": "in two different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125350.0,
      "end_time": 127320.0,
      "text": "One was we gave executives a long list"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127320.0,
      "end_time": 130902.0,
      "text": "of possible value drivers, things that create value"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130901.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132394.0,
      "text": "at their companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 132395.0,
      "end_time": 134818.0,
      "text": "And we asked them to rank those items."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134818.0,
      "end_time": 137799.0,
      "text": "And it turns corporate culture came out on top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137799.0,
      "end_time": 140606.0,
      "text": "the biggest value driver at companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140606.0,
      "end_time": 142501.0,
      "text": "More important than the strategic plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142501.0,
      "end_time": 145854.0,
      "text": "than the operating plan, more important than the CEO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145854.0,
      "end_time": 147432.0,
      "text": "and me a finance professor, more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147432.0,
      "end_time": 150793.0,
      "text": "than the finance function of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150794.0,
      "end_time": 152421.0,
      "text": "Okay, so corporate culture very important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 152421.0,
      "end_time": 154221.0,
      "text": "it came out on top."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154221.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "Not just in the United States but around the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 160462.0,
      "text": "In Africa, Europe, in Asia, in Latin America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160462.0,
      "end_time": 162631.0,
      "text": "we saw culture showing up as either number one"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162632.0,
      "end_time": 164673.0,
      "text": "or maybe a close second."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 164673.0,
      "end_time": 166438.0,
      "text": "So culture&#39;s very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166438.0,
      "end_time": 169275.0,
      "text": "Second way we addressed this is we just straight on asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169276.0,
      "end_time": 172600.0,
      "text": "\"How important is corporate culture at your firm?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172600.0,
      "end_time": 175800.0,
      "text": "And here about 90% of executives told us"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 178362.0,
      "text": "culture is either important or very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 178362.0,
      "end_time": 180680.0,
      "text": "And most of them said very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 180680.0,
      "end_time": 183680.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve established then that corporate culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183680.0,
      "end_time": 184462.0,
      "text": "is very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 184462.0,
      "end_time": 187420.0,
      "text": "The next question is what is it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187430.0,
      "end_time": 189446.0,
      "text": "What exactly is corporate culture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 189446.0,
      "end_time": 192850.0,
      "text": "So remember I told you we interviewed a lot of executives"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 192850.0,
      "end_time": 194548.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s a couple of interview quotes I&#39;d like to give you"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 194548.0,
      "end_time": 196477.0,
      "text": "to give you a sense of what culture is."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 196477.0,
      "end_time": 197864.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll paraphrase."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 197864.0,
      "end_time": 199489.0,
      "text": "The first is that corporate culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 199489.0,
      "end_time": 202145.0,
      "text": "is like the tendons in our body."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202145.0,
      "end_time": 204830.0,
      "text": "The tendons hold together the muscle and the bone"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 204830.0,
      "end_time": 207775.0,
      "text": "and they let our muscle and bone and body do the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207775.0,
      "end_time": 211474.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s intended to do in a healthy and productive way."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 211474.0,
      "end_time": 212732.0,
      "text": "Okay, like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 212732.0,
      "end_time": 216920.0,
      "text": "Culture is what helps the company reach it&#39;s potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 216920.0,
      "end_time": 218950.0,
      "text": "Okay, holds the company together, if you will."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 218950.0,
      "end_time": 222291.0,
      "text": "Another example is in the example of an orchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 222291.0,
      "end_time": 224590.0,
      "text": "Corporate culture is like sheet music."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 224590.0,
      "end_time": 228220.0,
      "text": "You can hire the best trumpet player, the best violinist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 228220.0,
      "end_time": 230686.0,
      "text": "and if they&#39;re not playing on the same sheet music"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 230686.0,
      "end_time": 232939.0,
      "text": "you won&#39;t get a very good outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232939.0,
      "end_time": 235499.0,
      "text": "But if you have the culture, if you have that sheet music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 235499.0,
      "end_time": 238117.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re playing in the same tempo, the same cadence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238117.0,
      "end_time": 240881.0,
      "text": "then you can have a wonderful outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240882.0,
      "end_time": 243217.0,
      "text": "Likewise the culture is what helps a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 243217.0,
      "end_time": 244659.0,
      "text": "reach its potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 244659.0,
      "end_time": 247840.0,
      "text": "It helps the employees march together."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 247840.0,
      "end_time": 250602.0,
      "text": "So those interviews give us a nice idea of what culture is."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 250602.0,
      "end_time": 253790.0,
      "text": "But like true academics we want to put more structure on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 253790.0,
      "end_time": 256789.0,
      "text": "We wanted a little framework, a little model if you will."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 256790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260957.00000000003,
      "text": "So we relied on existing research and kind of built on that."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 261510.0,
      "end_time": 263679.0,
      "text": "And what existing research says is there&#39;s kind of two ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 263679.0,
      "end_time": 265443.0,
      "text": "you can break down a company."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265443.0,
      "end_time": 268772.0,
      "text": "One part is the formal institutions, okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 268773.0,
      "end_time": 271526.0,
      "text": "And these formal institutions are things you can write down:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 271526.0,
      "end_time": 275910.0,
      "text": "the governance of the company, the compensation policies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 275910.0,
      "end_time": 277579.0,
      "text": "the hiring and firing practices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 277579.0,
      "end_time": 280310.0,
      "text": "you know kind of tangible things."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 280310.0,
      "end_time": 281184.0,
      "text": "Those are important."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 281184.0,
      "end_time": 283700.0,
      "text": "People have done a lot of research on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283700.0,
      "end_time": 286116.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not researching them so much in this paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 286116.0,
      "end_time": 289366.0,
      "text": "On the other side, you have the informal aspects"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 289366.0,
      "end_time": 291683.0,
      "text": "that we call corporate culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 291683.0,
      "end_time": 293960.0,
      "text": "And culture has really two main components:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 293960.0,
      "end_time": 296371.0,
      "text": "the values and the norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 296372.0,
      "end_time": 298241.0,
      "text": "Okay, a little lingo."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 298241.0,
      "end_time": 300972.0,
      "text": "But the values, they&#39;re sort of like the 10 commandments."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 300972.0,
      "end_time": 303248.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re chiseled on stone."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 303249.0,
      "end_time": 307416.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re the things we aspire to, that we&#39;d like to achieve."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 307734.0,
      "end_time": 310750.0,
      "text": "But the norms are actually the day-to-day living"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 310750.0,
      "end_time": 313625.0,
      "text": "as we strive to reach those values."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 313625.0,
      "end_time": 316947.0,
      "text": "And one of the main contributions of our paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 316947.0,
      "end_time": 320820.0,
      "text": "in the academic sense at least, is to kind of provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 320820.0,
      "end_time": 323283.0,
      "text": "evidence that these norms are very very important:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 323283.0,
      "end_time": 326560.0,
      "text": "the day-to-day living of the values."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 326560.0,
      "end_time": 328813.0,
      "text": "In fact, we&#39;re one of the few papers to focus on norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 328813.0,
      "end_time": 332163.0,
      "text": "And our conclusion is, without the norms the values"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 332163.0,
      "end_time": 334838.0,
      "text": "and these other things don&#39;t matter very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 334838.0,
      "end_time": 338712.0,
      "text": "You can look at a recent editorial by the former CEO of IBM"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 338712.0,
      "end_time": 341365.0,
      "text": "in the editorials of the Wall Street Journal."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 341365.0,
      "end_time": 343124.0,
      "text": "And he says something very similar."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 343124.0,
      "end_time": 346777.0,
      "text": "Values, you look along websites you see very similar values"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 346777.0,
      "end_time": 348154.0,
      "text": "across companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 348154.0,
      "end_time": 352320.0,
      "text": "But the norms, where the feet hit the ground if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 352327.0,
      "end_time": 355413.0,
      "text": "the living out of the values, the norms that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 355413.0,
      "end_time": 357697.0,
      "text": "is really what matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 357697.0,
      "end_time": 359780.0,
      "text": "So how does culture work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 360750.0,
      "end_time": 364404.0,
      "text": "You need to have values, norms, and these formal things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 364404.0,
      "end_time": 367590.0,
      "text": "the compensation policy for example, working together"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 367590.0,
      "end_time": 370638.0,
      "text": "and reinforcing each other to actually achieve"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 370638.0,
      "end_time": 372539.0,
      "text": "an effective corporate culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 372540.0,
      "end_time": 375290.0,
      "text": "So you need all of these aligned."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 377672.0,
      "end_time": 380860.0,
      "text": "Now a little more detail, how does culture work."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 380860.0,
      "end_time": 382895.0,
      "text": "What we wouldn&#39;t want to do is think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 382895.0,
      "end_time": 386325.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, if I get a good culture, I&#39;ll get a good outcome.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 386325.0,
      "end_time": 387815.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;d rather have you think of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 387815.0,
      "end_time": 390192.0,
      "text": "as really a two-step process."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 390192.0,
      "end_time": 393213.0,
      "text": "The second step is, if I have an effective culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 393213.0,
      "end_time": 395554.0,
      "text": "I get the desired outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 395554.0,
      "end_time": 396958.0,
      "text": "But the first step, and the one"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 396959.0,
      "end_time": 398791.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re really more focused on, is"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398791.0,
      "end_time": 402957.0,
      "text": "\"What do we need to do to achieve that effective culture?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 403118.0,
      "end_time": 406799.0,
      "text": "And here it&#39;s really again the norms, the values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406799.0,
      "end_time": 410489.0,
      "text": "and these formal aspects like the compensation policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 410489.0,
      "end_time": 412649.0,
      "text": "and governance have to all work together"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 412649.0,
      "end_time": 415445.0,
      "text": "to give you an effective culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 415445.0,
      "end_time": 417894.0,
      "text": "And this is what we think companies should focus on a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 417894.0,
      "end_time": 421226.0,
      "text": "is what it takes to get an effective culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 421226.0,
      "end_time": 422665.0,
      "text": "What are some of the outcomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 422665.0,
      "end_time": 424841.0,
      "text": "from having an effective culture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 424841.0,
      "end_time": 427519.0,
      "text": "Or an ineffective culture as it might be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 427519.0,
      "end_time": 430680.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m gonna talk about four things briefly."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 430680.0,
      "end_time": 431224.0,
      "text": "If you look in the research paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 431225.0,
      "end_time": 434380.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s probably a dozen more outcomes you could talk about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 434380.0,
      "end_time": 435555.0,
      "text": "we could talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 435555.0,
      "end_time": 437955.0,
      "text": "One is investment risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 437955.0,
      "end_time": 439824.0,
      "text": "We just lived through a financial crisis:"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 439824.0,
      "end_time": 443969.0,
      "text": "a deep depression, or deep recession excuse me."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 443969.0,
      "end_time": 446360.0,
      "text": "And what we&#39;ve noticed is some companies seem"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 446360.0,
      "end_time": 448119.0,
      "text": "to take on too much risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 449458.0,
      "end_time": 453625.0,
      "text": "Now what the executives at these companies tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 453734.0,
      "end_time": 456181.0,
      "text": "is that having a bad culture is what leads to"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 456182.0,
      "end_time": 459341.0,
      "text": "companies taking on too much risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 459341.0,
      "end_time": 461427.0,
      "text": "A little surprising to us, a number of companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 461427.0,
      "end_time": 465230.0,
      "text": "told us their companies take on too little risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 465230.0,
      "end_time": 467519.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re too satisfied with the status quo."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 467519.0,
      "end_time": 470128.0,
      "text": "And again it&#39;s the culture isn&#39;t quite right"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 470128.0,
      "end_time": 474294.0,
      "text": "to encourage the company to take on entrepreneurial risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 474373.0,
      "end_time": 476401.0,
      "text": "So bottom line here on investment risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 476401.0,
      "end_time": 478166.0,
      "text": "is if you have an effective culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 478166.0,
      "end_time": 482680.0,
      "text": "you take the appropriate amount of investment risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 482680.0,
      "end_time": 484120.0,
      "text": "Alright, ethics."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 484120.0,
      "end_time": 488179.0,
      "text": "85% of executives tell us that when the culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 489940.0,
      "end_time": 492179.0,
      "text": "is not right, it can lead to unethical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 492179.0,
      "end_time": 496135.0,
      "text": "or even illegal, actions by employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 496136.0,
      "end_time": 498676.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not just the headlines that we read about."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 498676.0,
      "end_time": 502890.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually 85% of executives saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 502890.0,
      "end_time": 504480.0,
      "text": "they need to get the culture right at their company"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 504480.0,
      "end_time": 506131.0,
      "text": "or things could go sour."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 507400.0,
      "end_time": 509827.0,
      "text": "Third, short-term versus long-term."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 509827.0,
      "end_time": 512220.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it&#39;s said that in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 512220.0,
      "end_time": 514369.0,
      "text": "companies focus too much on the short-term"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 514369.0,
      "end_time": 516762.0,
      "text": "and they should focus more on the long-term."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 516760.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519173.99999999994,
      "text": "Again, executives tell us that when they have"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 519174.0,
      "end_time": 522138.0,
      "text": "the bad outcome focus too much on the short-term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 522138.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524494.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s cause the culture&#39;s not working right."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 524494.0,
      "end_time": 526991.0,
      "text": "When they have the good outcome focusing on the long-term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 526991.0,
      "end_time": 529196.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s because the culture is working right."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 529196.0,
      "end_time": 531189.0,
      "text": "They have an effective culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 531189.0,
      "end_time": 534113.0,
      "text": "And then finally, let me give you a more specific example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 534114.0,
      "end_time": 536710.0,
      "text": "mergers and acquisitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 536710.0,
      "end_time": 539654.0,
      "text": "Very important investment decision if you will."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 539654.0,
      "end_time": 543456.0,
      "text": "So here we ask if your company has a target company in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 543456.0,
      "end_time": 546770.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s very aligned on the operational side"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 546770.0,
      "end_time": 550343.0,
      "text": "and the target&#39;s doing just what you want it to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 550343.0,
      "end_time": 552706.0,
      "text": "to acquire it and bring it into your company."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 552706.0,
      "end_time": 555802.0,
      "text": "But the culture is not properly aligned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 555802.0,
      "end_time": 558261.0,
      "text": "so you have a misaligned culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 558261.0,
      "end_time": 561382.0,
      "text": "When that happens, we wanted to ask executives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 561382.0,
      "end_time": 563501.0,
      "text": "\"How much of a discount would you require"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 563501.0,
      "end_time": 566408.0,
      "text": "\"to acquire that target?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 566408.0,
      "end_time": 567842.0,
      "text": "And that would give us a sense of"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 567842.0,
      "end_time": 570330.0,
      "text": "just how important culture is."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 570330.0,
      "end_time": 572333.0,
      "text": "So misaligned culture, how much would that reduce"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 572333.0,
      "end_time": 574514.0,
      "text": "the price you&#39;re willing to pay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 574514.0,
      "end_time": 577719.0,
      "text": "And we thought we&#39;d hear maybe 15%, 20%."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 577719.0,
      "end_time": 580708.0,
      "text": "In fact, the main thing we heard is most companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 580708.0,
      "end_time": 584570.0,
      "text": "wouldn&#39;t pursue an acquisition at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 584570.0,
      "end_time": 586217.0,
      "text": "if the culture is misaligned."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 586217.0,
      "end_time": 588829.0,
      "text": "So that kind of tells us just how important culture is"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 588829.0,
      "end_time": 592190.0,
      "text": "in general; but also, in the M and A context, how important"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 592191.0,
      "end_time": 596358.0,
      "text": "it is to align the cultures before you proceed."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 596874.0,
      "end_time": 599557.0,
      "text": "Alright, let me give you a little more detail here"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 599557.0,
      "end_time": 603215.0,
      "text": "on some of the statistical stuff we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 603215.0,
      "end_time": 605387.0,
      "text": "So far I&#39;ve been at pretty high level."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 605387.0,
      "end_time": 608214.0,
      "text": "So we ran regressions where we tried to explain"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 608214.0,
      "end_time": 611101.0,
      "text": "how does a company get an effective corporate culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 611101.0,
      "end_time": 613601.0,
      "text": "that would lead to creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 614501.0,
      "end_time": 615564.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s think of creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 615564.0,
      "end_time": 617873.0,
      "text": "or innovation you might call it."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 617874.0,
      "end_time": 620212.0,
      "text": "Well the value that is going to lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 620212.0,
      "end_time": 622790.0,
      "text": "to creativity is adaptability."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 622791.0,
      "end_time": 625151.0,
      "text": "So a company that has a value where it can react"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 625151.0,
      "end_time": 628646.0,
      "text": "as times change and as the environment changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 628647.0,
      "end_time": 631902.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a value that leads to creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 631902.0,
      "end_time": 634352.0,
      "text": "But, as we said before, it&#39;s not just the value"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 634352.0,
      "end_time": 636981.0,
      "text": "that matters, it&#39;s also the norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 636981.0,
      "end_time": 640900.0,
      "text": "So what are the norms that lead to creativity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 640900.0,
      "end_time": 642223.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s developing new ideas organically"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 642223.0,
      "end_time": 645541.0,
      "text": "within your company, and the employees having comfort"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 645542.0,
      "end_time": 648448.0,
      "text": "in offering and receiving critiques."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 648448.0,
      "end_time": 650226.0,
      "text": "If that&#39;s the work environment you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 650226.0,
      "end_time": 653956.0,
      "text": "on a day-to-day basis where you are developing"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 653956.0,
      "end_time": 657297.0,
      "text": "new ideas organically and giving and accepting critiques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 657297.0,
      "end_time": 660899.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the environment that leads to creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 660899.0,
      "end_time": 663782.0,
      "text": "Now interestingly, there&#39;s another value that was listed"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 663782.0,
      "end_time": 666284.0,
      "text": "but had a negative effect on creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 666284.0,
      "end_time": 670103.0,
      "text": "When a company is really results driven, results oriented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 670103.0,
      "end_time": 672625.0,
      "text": "maybe too focused on the bottom line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 672625.0,
      "end_time": 674684.0,
      "text": "that does not lead to creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 674684.0,
      "end_time": 676448.0,
      "text": "It actually hurts it."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 676448.0,
      "end_time": 679174.0,
      "text": "Alright, second example, ethics."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 679174.0,
      "end_time": 682640.0,
      "text": "What value leads to ethical behavior?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 682640.0,
      "end_time": 684564.0,
      "text": "Well, integrity is such a value."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 684565.0,
      "end_time": 687870.0,
      "text": "That sounds wonderful, but what are the norms"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 687870.0,
      "end_time": 689365.0,
      "text": "that are required, the day-to-day living"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 689365.0,
      "end_time": 693255.0,
      "text": "that is required in order to achieve that value"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 693255.0,
      "end_time": 695764.0,
      "text": "and to achieve good ethical behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 695764.0,
      "end_time": 699829.0,
      "text": "Here, trust among employees is the most important norm"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 699829.0,
      "end_time": 702199.0,
      "text": "and also willingness of the employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 702200.0,
      "end_time": 704353.0,
      "text": "to report unethical behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 704353.0,
      "end_time": 707338.0,
      "text": "So if you have that happening in your work environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 707338.0,
      "end_time": 710901.0,
      "text": "you get the good positive ethical outcomes that you desire."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 710901.0,
      "end_time": 712660.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s a lot more detail in the paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 712660.0,
      "end_time": 714858.0,
      "text": "that you can look at if you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 714859.0,
      "end_time": 717721.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m just trying to give you a sampling today."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 717721.0,
      "end_time": 719987.0,
      "text": "Alright to summarize so far, corporate culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 719987.0,
      "end_time": 721848.0,
      "text": "is first order important."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 721849.0,
      "end_time": 725334.0,
      "text": "We think of culture as being made up of values and norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 725334.0,
      "end_time": 728688.0,
      "text": "The norms are the day-to-day living of those values."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 728688.0,
      "end_time": 731548.0,
      "text": "And we think of it in a two-step process with the values"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 731548.0,
      "end_time": 734889.0,
      "text": "and norms working together along with other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 734889.0,
      "end_time": 737793.0,
      "text": "like compensation policy give you an effective culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 737793.0,
      "end_time": 739769.0,
      "text": "which gives you the outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 739769.0,
      "end_time": 743355.0,
      "text": "So that sounds all nice, but do all companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 743355.0,
      "end_time": 744854.0,
      "text": "have effective cultures?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 744854.0,
      "end_time": 746746.0,
      "text": "If it&#39;s that easy, does everyone achieve it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 746746.0,
      "end_time": 748117.0,
      "text": "No they don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 748117.0,
      "end_time": 750307.0,
      "text": "About 15% of companies tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 750307.0,
      "end_time": 753930.0,
      "text": "they have their culture right where they want it."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 753930.0,
      "end_time": 754269.0,
      "text": "The rest don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 754269.0,
      "end_time": 756207.0,
      "text": "And in fact about a third of companies tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 756207.0,
      "end_time": 759238.0,
      "text": "they need to have a considerable work"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 759238.0,
      "end_time": 762310.0,
      "text": "or substantial overhaul to get their culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 762310.0,
      "end_time": 763708.0,
      "text": "to where they need it to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 763708.0,
      "end_time": 765307.0,
      "text": "So about a third of companies say they have"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 765307.0,
      "end_time": 767201.0,
      "text": "a lot of work to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 767201.0,
      "end_time": 769906.0,
      "text": "How do you improve your corporate culture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 769906.0,
      "end_time": 772387.0,
      "text": "Alright, starts with leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 772387.0,
      "end_time": 774277.0,
      "text": "The leaders must define the culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 774278.0,
      "end_time": 778150.0,
      "text": "and they must live those corporate and cultural values."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 778150.0,
      "end_time": 779984.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not talking about the board of directors."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 779984.0,
      "end_time": 782557.0,
      "text": "The board of directors hires the CEO."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 782557.0,
      "end_time": 784987.0,
      "text": "But the CEO and the leadership team are the ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 784987.0,
      "end_time": 789640.0,
      "text": "that instill that corporate culture into the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 789650.0,
      "end_time": 790452.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s very important that the culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 790452.0,
      "end_time": 793840.0,
      "text": "permeate the mid-level management"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 793840.0,
      "end_time": 795440.0,
      "text": "and the rank and file employees also,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 795440.0,
      "end_time": 797370.0,
      "text": "or of course it&#39;s not going to succeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 797370.0,
      "end_time": 800737.0,
      "text": "So we need employees of all levels to buy in"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 800737.0,
      "end_time": 803976.0,
      "text": "and to live the culture on a day-to-day basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 803976.0,
      "end_time": 808103.0,
      "text": "Second point, the company must invest in corporate culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 808103.0,
      "end_time": 811775.0,
      "text": "It must dedicate time and resources to instill"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 811775.0,
      "end_time": 814803.0,
      "text": "and to reinforce the culture at the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 814803.0,
      "end_time": 817351.0,
      "text": "So this involves recognizing when employees act"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 817351.0,
      "end_time": 819695.0,
      "text": "in a way that&#39;s in accordance with the culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 819695.0,
      "end_time": 822212.0,
      "text": "celebrating those achievements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 822212.0,
      "end_time": 825339.0,
      "text": "and even having promotional and hiring decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 825339.0,
      "end_time": 829506.0,
      "text": "based on achieving the culture of the firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 829624.0,
      "end_time": 833400.0,
      "text": "And finally, this is a continuous, long-term commitment"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 833400.0,
      "end_time": 834301.0,
      "text": "by the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 834301.0,
      "end_time": 835402.0,
      "text": "This is not something you achieve"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 835402.0,
      "end_time": 837235.0,
      "text": "in a weekend retreat somewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 837235.0,
      "end_time": 839393.0,
      "text": "This has to be happening week after week at the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 839393.0,
      "end_time": 843292.0,
      "text": "to really get the culture to where you need it to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 843292.0,
      "end_time": 846685.0,
      "text": "So I told you at the beginning, I started as a skeptic."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 846685.0,
      "end_time": 848734.0,
      "text": "Well our research team has concluded that culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 848735.0,
      "end_time": 850763.0,
      "text": "is in fact very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 850763.0,
      "end_time": 852322.0,
      "text": "And I hope I&#39;ve been able to convey to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 852322.0,
      "end_time": 855297.0,
      "text": "some of the ways that culture works at the firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 855297.0,
      "end_time": 858100.0,
      "text": "I got two research papers out there that you can look up"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 858100.0,
      "end_time": 859981.0,
      "text": "if you want more details."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 859981.0,
      "end_time": 862755.0,
      "text": "The first paper has a lot of the statistical analysis"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 862755.0,
      "end_time": 864400.0,
      "text": "from survey results."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 864400.0,
      "end_time": 867870.0,
      "text": "The second focuses on the interviews."
    }
  ]
}